headline: CBRE Group (NYSE:CBRE): A Bullish Investment Perspective
summary: We came across a bullish thesis on CBRE Group Inc. (CBRE) on ValueInvestorsClub by beethoven. In this article, we will summarize the bulls’ thesis on CBRE. CBRE’s stock was trading at $90.38 when this thesis was published, vs. a closing price of $129.40 on November 7. CBRE is the world’s leading commercial real estate and investment company […]
